msgstr "生成一个key文件:"

#: ../source/includes/steps/enable-authentication-in-sharded-cluster.rst:11
msgid ""
"Create the key file your deployment will use to authenticate servers to each "
"other."
msgstr "生成服务器之间进行权限认证时的key文件."

